Comment.val:
/*Crritical check: checks wheter the the version in the database (TABELGEGEVEN SYST 7050) matches the version in the MAGIC.INI.
The repstr-construction in the AddError parameter was nescessarry because XPA does not support the use of dots in pictures*/

Text.val: Data from the Magic.INI, provided by the installer
This value is updated by a SQL script, procecessed by the installion of a release/patch
For Example : 07.04.02.01 (emergency-patch) 1 on patch 2 of release 7.4
We only check when syst 7050 Exists
when the versionnr doesn't match error.

ExpSyntax.val: StrBuild(MlsTrans('Het versienummer @1@ uit de magic.ini komt niet overeen met de versie @2@ uit de database !'),RepStr(Str({0,2}*10000+{0,12},'##|##|##|##P0'),'|','.'),RepStr(Str({0,9}*10000+{0,13},'##|##|##|##P0'),'|','.'))
